{"tid":864211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【腳變S形慘死】7歲仔爬木雕被壓死 家長大控訴網民咁反應","createTime":"2018-10-16T04:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T05:43:43.000Z","uid":29161,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7e53618c06071b805fe4de75ae60a7f3fc25a0b3","tid":864211,"uid":29161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:42:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181016/58799210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58799210&d=cEAnvk2AvDxxfsjQNXhyCsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3fd71d5c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181016%2F58799210&h=449d4a18\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181016/58799210</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n父母看漏一眼，可能從此痛失小孩！浙江省義烏市義烏國際貿易城日前便上演了令人痛心的一幕，一名體重僅40斤的7歲男童，疑因頑皮攀爬一座高2米、重數噸的柚木雕像，致雕像倒下，當場被壓死。現場影片可見，其左腳扭曲成詭異的S形，臉朝地趴在血泊中，母親隨後緊抱男童遺體崩潰痛哭。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n據內地媒體報道，義烏國際貿易城事後發佈聲明指，13日上午10時30分許在貿易城五區地下進口城，發生一宗男童攀爬柚木雕塑，致雕塑倒地壓到小孩的事件，工作人員隨即前往醫院協助。公司對此事件深表痛心，將加強貿易城安全隱患檢查，並提醒商戶在經商的同時，看護好身邊的小孩。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n不過，據鳳凰網報道，家屬事後不滿貿易城處理的方式，在微信發文並po出現場影片作出控訴，指木雕沒有任何保護措施、嚴重搖晃，將孩子當場砸死，又指商場推卸責任、封鎖消息，強調「類似的事情在義烏市場屢見不鮮，每年發生數起，是否是因為我們孩童生命輕如草芥，才使得市場方如此輕率，如此瀆職」，呼籲大家轉發訊息，意圖以輿論壓力讓商場屈服，但完全沒提是男童攀爬木雕造成慘劇。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n不少網民看到是頑童攀爬肇禍，紛紛留言「首先要管好自個小孩，不能一出事就追究別人的責任」、「孩子攀爬造成的，我覺得不應該賠」、「雕塑摔壞沒有？摔壞了讓他賠。現在的小孩基本被家人寵得沒教養」、「教育不好，遲早是要受到懲罰的，現在才來哭、來指着別人」。但也有人認為，一名男童就能弄倒的木雕，恐怕重心並不穩，沒有護欄保護實在不妥，商場應該也要負責任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181016/large/1539656773_b726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181016%2Flarge%2F1539656773_b726.jpg&h=645d89c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd74229a3e9da1e44a78089c4b6cbf4adc26ffa7","tid":864211,"uid":5384,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:44:45.000Z","msg":"安已不"},{"pid":"92145223761afaed59101e37003fb108f08a61a8","tid":864211,"uid":24265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:44:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱</span></span>"},{"pid":"a125f49631541f8e02a25168394f9351be269916","tid":864211,"uid":42188,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee46e2716085ea8ae4d3a914546b97f96ca437f8","tid":864211,"uid":3117,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:47:22.000Z","msg":"希望個木雕無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f9362e42da698c70add520fc5b1af033ab6cc43","tid":864211,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a125f49631541f8e02a25168394f9351be269916","tid":864211,"uid":42188,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"好治癒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"0c310904130ed7818f91d0fb44f7750ad15b4130","tid":864211,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"Sor射左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69505aaeed1598a1c9a76a827918ad4e936b46c1","tid":864211,"uid":193364,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個木雕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1081f1531ea00000c1d6a972f51573450887f58d","tid":864211,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ee46e2